wer><Date type="date" label="Date" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true" display="localdateshort" UTC="true">20121128T19:00:00</Date><Author type="string" label="Author's Name" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Hayden Coombs</Author><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Height=""><![CDATA[Brother Fenton Broadhead announced that Kirk Widdison will serve as the new chair of the Languages and International Studies Department. He will be replacing Scott Galer, who will be serving in a new role with Foundations and Interdisciplinary Studies. This assignment will take effect January 1.<br /><br /> "I would like to extend a heartfelt thanks to Scott Galer and hope that you will join me in expressing sincere appreciation for the service he has given to the department and university.&nbsp; We wish him great success in his new role with Foundations &amp; Interdisciplinary Studies." Brother Broadhead said. <br /><br />"Thank you for the feedback many of you have given and the confidence you have shown for Kirk.&nbsp; We hope that you will support him as he represents each of you."]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="Component" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="x35693" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Name="News" label="News" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="NewsNavigationComponent"/><xPower Type="List" Name="ContentSnippet" label="Content Snippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="" List=""><xPower Type="Component" Name="xPower" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes=""/></xPower><xPower Type="Navigation" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false" Navigation="Ancestors" GenerationOrder="down" StartPage="x5" MaxNodes="" MaxDepth="" Query